          "slidecontent": "• AI tools can support materials selection but must never replace professional judgement on compliance and safety\n• Always verify AI-generated recommendations against current British Standards and local building regulations\n• Durability and environmental suitability require site-specific knowledge that AI alone cannot provide\n• Cross-check outputs with suppliers, engineers, or certified specialists\n• Document every AI-assisted decision for audit and accountability purposes\n• As a next step, identify one materials decision in your current project where you could trial an AI tool alongside your usual verification process"
